Privacy Policy
Our Privacy Policy describes the information collected by NellaSoft through our mobile applications and the use of the information.
We do not collect any personal information with our Apps
When you download and use our mobile applications, we don’t require you to provide any personal information and we don’t collect any personal information about you. Some non-personal information may be collected by third-party service Unity analytics, such as: unique device identifiers, IP address; device manufacturer and model platform type. You may check the detail privacy-policy of third-party company Unity from:
https://unity3d.com/legal/privacy-policy
We comply with the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act
Our mobile applications comply with the Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (“COPPA”). We don’t knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13, and if in the event that a user identifies himself or herself as a child under the age of 13 through a support request or through any feedback, we will not collect, store or use, and will delete in a secure manner, any personal information of such user.
Contact Us
If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please send us an email: developer@nellasoft.com
